```{r}
# https://github.com/dratnadiwakara/depositor-chars/blob/main/bank_branch_visits_count_2019_2022.rds.Rmd
branch_visits <- readRDS('data/bank_branch_visits_count_2019_2022.rds')
branch_visits[,yr:=year(DATE_RANGE_START)]



branch_df_2019 <- reg_sample[yr==2019,c("RSSDID","UNINUMBR","bank_assets","distance_from_home_km_2019","large_bank","sophisticated","zip","RUCA1")]
# branch_df_2019[,yr:=NULL]
branch_df_2019 <- merge(branch_df_2019,branch_visits,by="UNINUMBR")

begin_date <- as.Date(paste0('2019-01-01'))
branch_df_2019[,months_since_201901:=time_length(interval(begin_date,DATE_RANGE_START),"months")]



controls <- reg_sample[,c("UNINUMBR","yr","lag_hmda_mtg_amt_gr","lag_county_gdp_gr","lag_cra_loan_amount_amt_lt_1m_gr",
                          "establishments_gr","payroll_gr","legacy_branch","deposit_gr_3yrs","same_zip_prior_3yr_branches",
                          "lag_branch_deposit_amount","age")]
controls <- controls[!duplicated(controls[,c("UNINUMBR","yr")])]

branch_df_2019 <- merge(branch_df_2019,controls,by=c("UNINUMBR","yr"))

branch_df_2019[,post_2020:=ifelse(yr>2020,1,0)]
branch_df_2019[,calendar_month:=month(DATE_RANGE_START)]
```


```{r}
var <- "sophisticated" #,"log(median_income)","pct_college_educated","median_age","has_dividend_income_pct"

plots <- list()

control_vars <- "+age+I(lag_hmda_mtg_amt_gr/100)+I(lag_county_gdp_gr/100)+I(lag_cra_loan_amount_amt_lt_1m_gr/100)+establishments_gr+payroll_gr+legacy_branch+I(deposit_gr_3yrs/100)+same_zip_prior_3yr_branches+log(lag_branch_deposit_amount)+log(distance_from_home_km_2019)|calendar_month+yr+RSSDID+zip|0|RSSDID"

controls_plots <- paste0("*factor(months_since_201901)",control_vars)
controls_reg <- paste0("*post_2020",control_vars)
```



## Number of unique visitors

```{r}
dep_var <- "log(RAW_VISITOR_COUNTS+1)"
```


### Regression
```{r}
#| eval: true
r <- list()
r[[1]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0(dep_var,'~',var,controls_reg)),data=branch_df_2019[large_bank==1])
r[[2]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0(dep_var,'~',var,controls_reg)),data=branch_df_2019[large_bank==0])

stargazer(r,
          type="text",
          no.space = T,
          dep.var.labels.include = F,
          column.labels = c("Large","Small"),
          column.separate = c(1,1),
          model.names = F,
          omit.stat = c("ser","adj.rsq"),
          add.lines = list(
                           c("Bank FE",rep("Y",13)),
                           c("ZIP FE",rep(c("Y"),13)),
                           c("Month FE",rep("Y",13))
                           )
          )
```

### Diff-in-diff plots

```{r}
#| eval: true
r <- list()
r[[1]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0(dep_var,'~',var,controls_plots)),data=branch_df_2019[large_bank==1])
r[[2]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0(dep_var,'~',var,controls_plots)),data=branch_df_2019[large_bank==0])


  
p1 <- coef_plot_1reg_10ci(r[[1]],paste0(var,":factor(months_since_201901)"),
            min(branch_df_2019$months_since_201901))+
           ggtitle("Large Banks >100bn")+
          scale_x_continuous(labels = format(unique(branch_df_2019$DATE_RANGE_START),"%y-%m"),
                               breaks=unique(branch_df_2019$months_since_201901))


p2 <- coef_plot_1reg_10ci(r[[2]],paste0(var,":factor(months_since_201901)"),
                min(branch_df_2019$months_since_201901))+
               ggtitle(ggtitle("Small Banks <100bn"))+
              scale_x_continuous(labels = format(unique(branch_df_2019$DATE_RANGE_START),"%y-%m"),
                                   breaks=unique(branch_df_2019$months_since_201901))


grid.arrange(p1,p2)
```
